{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GVMmRrRQ7HZAGSDeWSkZP5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ray versions match (2.9.0). The issue is that `ray.init(address='ray-head:6379')` is connecting to an existing cluster but the ray-client is running `ray start` without being part of the cluster. When `ray.init(address=...)` is called with an address, it should connect to the existing cluster's GCS (Global Control Store). \n\nThe error is strange - `Can't find a node_ip_address.json file` suggests that the ray-client tried to start a Ray session locally but couldn't find the node file. Let me look at this more carefully.\nThe session timestamp in the error matches the current execution time, not a previous session, which means Ray is attempting a local connection before trying to reach the cluster. When connecting to a remote cluster via `ray.init(address='ray-head:6379')`, it shouldn't be creating a local session at all—it should go straight to the cluster's GCS. The fact that it's generating a new session directory suggests something's preventing the remote connection from working properly. Ray Client protocol works differently in Ray 2.x - using `ray://host:port` connects through the client server, while direct GCS connection with `ray://host:6379` tries to launch a local raylet on the client pod, which is why it's failing to find the node IP address file. The ray-client pod needs either the Ray Client protocol with the proper port or an environment variable to connect without being a full cluster node. So the validation command is using `ray.init(address='ray-head:6379')` to connect to the GCS directly, which should work in Ray 2.9.0 - the driver runs locally and connects to the existing cluster. The error about the local raylet failing to start suggests something's preventing it from initializing. I should check the head pod logs to see if the cluster itself is running properly.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":579,"cache_read_input_tokens":31928,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":579},"output_tokens":33,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6173f3b5-1b47-46a0-8403-5971b0c6fd75","uuid":"1e2a5bc0-3c4f-404a-b2d0-af5a04571683","request_id":"req_011CcL9dGSAHazqq73Kq9Jhs"}
